Parliament, Thursday, 13 September 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Home Affairs will today continue with the second phase of the investigation into the process followed in the naturalisation of the Gupta family. The committee will listen to evidence by the following individuals; Details of the Meeting Date: 13 September 2018
